===Video game===
A [[PlayStation Vita]] simulation game by [[Bandai Namco Games]] titled ''The Asterisk War: Houka Kenran'' was released in Japan on January 28, 2016.<ref>http://gematsu.com/2015/09/asterisk-war-ps-vita-game-launches-january-28-japan</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://gematsu.com/2015/08/asterisk-war-ps-vita-game-announced|title=The Asterisk War PS Vita game announced|website=Gematsu|date=August 22, 2015}}</ref>

